ill resume walking in the same\ndirection as before the fall. Being bumped while falling does not affect\nthe walking direction, and being bumped in the same cycle as ground\ndisappears (but not yet falling), or when the ground reappears while\nstill falling, also does not affect the walking direction.\n\nImplement a Moore state machine that models this behaviour. areset is\npositive edge triggered asynchronous reseting the Lemming machine to walk\nleft. Assume all sequential logic is triggered on the positive edge of\nthe clock.\n\n\n</input_spec>\n<failed_sim_log>\n{\n    "stdout": "",\n    "stderr": "./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:7: syntax error\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:1: Errors in port declarations.\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:16: warning: implicit definition of wire \'areset\'.\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:77: syntax error\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:77: error: Malformed statement\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:80: syntax error\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:82: error: Malformed statement\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:84: syntax error\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:85: error: Malformed statement\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:86: syntax error\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:86: error: Malformed statement\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:87: syntax error\\n./output_t22c_qwen3coder30b_shard4_0/VERILOG_EVAL_V2_Prob142_lemmings2/tb.sv:87: error: Malformed statement\\n./output_t22c_qwen3co